---
title: Coconut & Chermoula Veggie Soup with Cashew Nuts & Roasted Pumpkin
description: There’s something special about settling down after a long day with a warm aromatic soup. We’re leaning
into the comfort factor by roasting the veggies and adding them to the chermoula creamy soup. Garnish with
roasted cashew nuts and you’re in for a nutritious and relaxing night.

